Privacy Policy
We, Giga Fun Studios Private Limited (the “
Company”, “we”, “our” or “us
”), incorporated under the Companies Act, 2013, having its registered office at No. 233, Opp to Park, Ideal Homes, Bengaluru, Karnataka 560098, India, provides videogaming services (“
Services
”) through the website
www.gigafunstudios.com
, and associated mobile applications (“
Platform
”).
This Privacy Policy (defined below) applies to the usage of the Platform by users, which includes any user who is accessing the Platform (“
you
” or “
your
”). We ensure our firm commitment to your privacy vis-à-vis the protection of your information. In order to provide you with access to the Platform and use of our Services, we may collect, process and, in some circumstances, disclose information about you. We have created and notified this privacy policy (“
Privacy Policy
”) to set out the practices and procedure we will follow regarding the collection, use, storage and disclosure of any personally identifiable information provided by you to us in order to avail of our Services (“
Personal Information
”). This Privacy Policy has been drafted in accordance with the applicable laws, including the Information Technology Act, 2000, and the Information Technology (Reasonable security practices and procedures and sensitive personal data or information) Rules, 2011.
​
CONSENT
All visitors to the Platform are advised to read and understand our Privacy Policy carefully, as by accessing the Platform and availing the Services you agree to be bound by the terms and conditions set out in this Privacy Policy, and consent to the collection, storage and use of information relating to you, including transfer of your information to third-party partners, as provided herein. This Privacy Policy represents a binding agreement between you and the Company in accordance with the provisions of the Information Technology Act, 2000.
If you do not agree with the terms and conditions of our Privacy Policy, including in relation to the manner of collection or use of your information, please do not use or access the Platform.
If you have any questions or concerns regarding this privacy policy, you should contact our Customer Support Desk at
support@gigafunstudios.com
.
We reserve the right to change and/or update the terms and conditions of this Privacy Policy from time to time as we deem fit. We will endeavour to provide notice of any changes to you, however, you are required to periodically review the Privacy Policy from time to time for the latest information on our privacy practices. Should it be that you do not accept any of the modifications or amendments to the Privacy Policy, you should terminate your use of this Website immediately.
