COLLECTION OF INFORMATION
General Information
During your use of the Platform, we may collect such information from you including but not limited to:
your name;
your e-mail address;
your contact number;
your date of birth;
information derived from your social media access permissions;
your gamer tags;
your location;
your game account details and game progress;
your Mobile device identifiers and IP address;
your device data like the device name, operating system, and language;
coarse location (as suggested by your IP address);
your gameplay data and/or interactions with other players inside the Service;
application performance and de-bugging information; and
information regarding your browsing behaviour and pages visited via cookies and associated technology;
​
Data Collected from and Transferred to our Partners
We also use third-party partners, such as social networking sites, advertising networks, and data analytics providers, and we may collect or transfer your information from/to such third-party partners, including but not limited to:
Your location;
Your game account details, game events and game progress;
Your mobile device identifiers and IP address;
Your device data like the device name, operating system, and language;
Coarse location (as suggested by your IP address);
Your gameplay data and/or interactions with other players inside the Service;
Application performance and de-bugging information;
Data made available by you via your privacy settings in third-party services like Facebook, Google, Apple;
Demographic data (such as to determine the coarse location of your IP address);
Data to fight fraud related to refund or advertising;
Data from platforms that the games run on (such as purchase data to verify payments); and
Additional information (such as data for advertising and analytics purposes) to help display more relevant ads for you and improve the services we provide.
​
​
By accessing the Platform and availing the Services offered by us, you agree and acknowledge that the foregoing information may be transferred to and processed by our third-party partners.
The information we collect about you will depend on the Services that we offer, on an ongoing basis. To the extent possible, we provide you the option of not divulging any specific information that you wish for us not to collect, store or use. You may also choose not to use a particular Service or feature on the Platform, and opt out of any non-essential communications from the Company. Please note that if you do not allow us to collect all the information we request on the Platform, then we may not be able to deliver your chosen Services effectively. By using the Services, you consent to our retaining all the above-described information in anonymous form as long as we see fit. We may also retain personal information for an additional period as is permitted or required under applicable laws, for legal, tax, or regulatory reasons, or for legitimate and lawful business purposes.
​
USE BY CHILDREN
Children Under the Age of 13
We do not knowingly collect or solicit personal information from anyone under the age of 13 or knowingly allow such persons to register. If you are under 13, please do not attempt to register with us or send any information about yourself to us, including your name, address, telephone number, or email address. No one under age 13 may provide any personal information to us. In the event that we learn that we have collected personal information from a child under age 13 we will delete that information as quickly as possible. If you believe that we might have any information from or about a child under 13, please contact us at
support@gigafunstudios.com
.
Children Between the Ages of 13 and 18
We recommend that minors over the age of 13 ask their parents or legal guardians for permission before sending any information about themselves to anyone over the Internet.
