OPT-OUT OP
TIONS
Push Notifications
​
You may opt-out from receiving our push-notifications by changing the settings on your mobile device.
​
Opt-Out of Targeted Advertising
You can opt-out of interest-based advertising by following the privacy settings of your Android, iOS or Amazon device and selecting "Limit Ad Tracking." You can also opt-out by turning off “personalized ads” on Apple iOS, or "Opt-out of Interest Based Ads" on Android, or by disabling Interest based Ads on Amazon.
You can choose to agree or disagree with us sharing your personal data for displaying targeted ads depending on which platform you play our games:
iOS: Choose from the consent pop-up at the start of the game (if you haven’t already generally disabled tracking in your system settings).
Android: Opt out of ad tracking by going to Settings > Ads > Opt out of Ads Personalization.
If you would like more information about advertising practices and to know your choices about not having this information used by these companies, you can visit Apple/Google's Advertising and Privacy page or the
Network Advertising Initiative
. Please understand that if you disable or block certain ad features, then other aspects of our mobile games may not work correctly.
